Name: Print Platform
Design Intend: The print platform is a crucial component which bridge the z-axis subsystem, recoater subsystem - and the powder handling system via the recoater. The shielding-gas cross flow also emerge from the platform. The alignment and perpendicularity of the z-axis is controlled by the platform - the fit in the hole should be a nice transistion or clearance fit with little to no play. The top surface should be flat and with low roughness.
